|CKBStreet Samurai Prices|000

|CKBHardware purchases|000
|CK0Rin Kade and Othra Veyr show the authoritative live price for every
unlocked signature implant. Engage the ripperdoc, open the Street Samurai
catalog, choose an implant and grade, and review its slot, strain, Guild Level,
hardware price, and separate procedure quote before confirming anything.|000

|CK0No single Street Samurai signature implant costs more than 100,000 coins in
the guild catalog. Earlier implants and lower grades scale below that ceiling.
The contract covers services, not purchases: buying hardware still costs the
listed amount and places the item in your inventory.|000

|CKBInstallation, extraction, and repair|000
|CK0An active Street Samurai contract waives installation and extraction fees
with Rin Kade in the guild clinic. Rin also repairs Street Samurai signature
hardware integrity without a labor charge. A paused or former contract does not
receive those benefits.|000

|CK0Othra's public clinic charges 10,000 coins per point of strain to install
and 5,000 coins per point of strain to extract, with a one-point minimum for
either procedure. His dialogue always shows the exact fee and requires
confirmation before surgery.|000

|CK0Installation still requires an open internal location and enough strain
capacity. Extraction returns the hardware to inventory. Ripperdocs do not
perform procedures during combat.|000
